{"tid":1545474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜託各位記者","createTime":"2019-09-06T02:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T05:24:03.000Z","uid":178470,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b296f0d3c2d770363c264e95e1c45b0c738ee8f1","tid":1545474,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:25:54.000Z","msg":"唔好人地記者會一句831太子站冇死人<br />\n就唔繼續追問落去<br />\n人地玩語言偽術都唔係第一日<br />\n我地一定要繼續追問繼續施壓<br />\n壓力一大就容易出破綻<br />\n<br />\n1.如果831晚上冇死人，咁<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9月1日凌晨</strong></span>太子有冇死人<br />\n<br />\n2.有冇市民係由<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>太子站離開後死</strong></span>亡，例如隔離站<br />\n<br />\n3.當晚荃灣線，觀塘綫，港島線都提早停止服務，沿途各站有冇市民死亡<br />\n<br />\n4.點解當初數到10個傷者，事後會得返7個送院<br />\n<br />\n5.由於救護被拒絕入站，事前有冇轉移傷者去其他站<br />\n<br />\n6.如果當時警員堅持地鐵站冇傷者，但點解救護員抵達會數到10個傷者？係警察無法判斷傷者，定係警察證供不可信？<br />\n<br />\n7.如果當時明明有傷者到拒絕接受救護員施救，有冇可能造成更大的後遺症<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多，唔該記者jer住問，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">問到佢哋出破綻為止！！！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n推到比記者睇到"},{"pid":"f75609b94ff733a397504633454ebb5e628b2cf1","tid":1545474,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:26:03.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b0ec157a70a5632d30a8f1fea0c6357fe15d85f","tid":1545474,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:27:11.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"8388a2bc118e6d6c69f22553191066707c2b3f1c","tid":1545474,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"